Dear OEW Collaborator,

We appreciate your support and contribution to the Open Education Week.  Your submission will be reviewed shortly by the OEW Planning Committee.  We will notify you and send you the OEW badge once your submission has been approved and posted on the website. In the meantime please don't hesitate to contact us at info@openeducationweek.org if you have any questions or updates to your submission.

The Open Education Week is a community effort built on everyone's contributions.  Please visit the website (www.openeducationweek.org) regularly to see the latest updates and additions to the event.  Don't forget to take advantage of the downloadable promotional materials to promote your own events and help us spread the word out of OEW 2018.

Once again thank you for helping us make this event a global celebration of the Open Education Movement. We look forward to seeing you around throughout the week.

Many thanks,
OEW Planning Committee

